name: Full Day Yangon City Tour
description: Explore the Buddhist monuments and Burmese culture of Yangon during this 9-hour city tour. Stop by iconic religious sites like Shwedagon Pagoda, and discover other Yangon highlights including the Reclining Buddha at Chauk Htat Gyi, Bogyoke Market, Botataung Pagoda, and much more. Site entrance fees, lunch and round-trip hotel transport are included.
